33
00:03:09.430 --> 00:03:11.430
Mungkin sebuah kasus.

34
00:03:11.430 --> 00:03:13.130
"Buku Bekas"

35
00:03:13.130 --> 00:03:15.630
Pak, ada polisi di bawah.

36
00:03:15.630 --> 00:03:17.330
Baiklah.

37
00:03:17.330 --> 00:03:19.030
Aku akan segera ke sana.

38
00:03:20.630 --> 00:03:21.930
Aku akan pergi memeriksanya.

39
00:03:21.930 --> 00:03:23.030
Apa?

40
00:03:23.030 --> 00:03:26.030
Hei. Tunggu dulu, Conan!

41
00:03:26.030 --> 00:03:28.430
Tahan lift sebentar.

42
00:03:31.430 --> 00:03:32.430
"Muatan Maksimal: 7 orang, 450kg"

43
00:03:32.430 --> 00:03:34.930
Kita kelebihan muatan.

44
00:03:34.930 --> 00:03:36.530
Maksimal adalah tujuh orang.

45
00:03:36.530 --> 00:03:37.730
Satu.

46
