175
00:11:06.030 --> 00:11:08.330
narkoba.

176
00:11:08.330 --> 00:11:11.730
Di sini juga ada.

177
00:11:11.730 --> 00:11:13.130
Di sini juga.

178
00:11:13.130 --> 00:11:14.230
Dengan kata lain,

179
00:11:14.230 --> 00:11:17.730
